Hits_minus_FA.Description:
fMRI task. Hits minus false alarms performance score,
    adjusted for unbalanced number of old and new trials;
    score = (hits/old) - (FA/new)

associative_memScore.Description:
fMRI task. Score of associative memory performance adjusted
    for the number of false alarms;
    score = correct_source/(wrong_source+false_alarms)

dprime.Description:
fMRI task. Normalized metric of memory recognition performance
    accounting for hit and false alarm rates;
    dprime = Z_probabHit - Z_probabFA; 0 = chance level
